video2audio 

video2audio is a simple Bash script created to convert video files into audio files on the Linux (Debian/Ubuntu) operating system using the Ffmpeg software.

Install

To install video2audio, make sure you are in superuser (root) mode.

$ apt-get update -y
$ apt-get install git -y
$ git clone https://github.com/rofidoang03/video2audio
$ cd video2audio
$ chmod a+rwx install
$./install
